<item>
            <title>[HIVE-5695] PTest2 fix shutdown, duplicate runs, and add client retry</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-5695</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are three issues with the PTest2 framework at present:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) When a test crashes it doesn&apos;t shutdown the underlying executors quickly&lt;br/&gt;
2) If a jira has two patches uploaded say 20 minutes a part that jira will have two pre-commit runs executed&lt;br/&gt;
3) The client doesn&apos;t aggressively retry impotent operations leading to the client (i.e. jenkins) finishing before the test actually does&lt;/p&gt;</description>
